nodes.text: During the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire, the companion of an individual delivered artwork stolen from the Museum of Abstract Ingenuity to an art collector on Antar 4.
The art collector was first mentioned in the Crew Skill mission "Stolen Masterpieces", in BioWare and LucasArts' 2011 massively multiplayer online roleplaying video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
